tool_description: Generates SEPA XML files for credit transfer (SCT) or direct debits (SDD). You can also validate IBANs and generate mandates in PDF format.
title: SEPA XML Generator

api_list.name: validate-iban
api_list.description: Validates a set of IBANs. If valid, adds information about the bank that issued it, like BIC, bank name or country code.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://sepa-xml-generator1.p.rapidapi.com/api/v2/bank_accounts"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "sepa-xml-generator1.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())

api_list.name: retrieve-mandate
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://sepa-xml-generator1.p.rapidapi.com/api/v2/mandates/{reference}"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "sepa-xml-generator1.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
